nodes.title: Prompt
widgets_values: A vibrant, photorealistic 4K cinematic landscape photo capturing a bright midday scene in Paris at precisely 1:51 PM. The Eiffel Tower stands majestically in the background under a crystal-clear blue sky, bathed in warm sunlight. The Seine River flows gracefully in the foreground, reflecting the golden hues of the sun and creating a dynamic contrast against the urban backdrop. The camera angle is slightly elevated, offering a sweeping view of the iconic landmarks and bustling city life. The image is framed with a wide-angle lens to emphasize the grandeur of the scene, with soft natural lighting enhancing the vivid colors and textures. The overall tone is lively and immersive, capturing the essence of Parisian charm in stunning detail.
